<rdf:Description
    rdf:about="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/1481"
    trackback:ping="http://www.notapathetic.com/cgi-bin/trackback.cgi/1481"
    dc:title="I am not voting because we live in a..."
    dc:identifier="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/1481"
    dc:description="I am not voting because we live in a "formal" democracy not a "real" democracy. Political parties are reduced to little more than a handful of leaders who are totally out of touch with the needs of the people. Through..."
    dc:creator="NotApathetic.com"
